What is ``pyxs``?
-----------------

What is ``pyxs``? It's a pure Python XenStore client implementation, which
coveres all of the ``libxs`` features and adds some nice Pythonic sugar on
top of it.

Installation
------------

If you have `pip <https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable>`_ you can do the usual
``pip install pyxs``. Otherwise, download the source from
`GitHub <https://github.com/selectel/pyxs>`_ and run
``python setup.py install``.
